### Health check — auth excluded.
GET http://localhost:3005/api/health

### Login — auth excluded, returns a token.
POST http://localhost:3005/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@example.com" }

### Secret — needs Bearer admin-token-123.
GET http://localhost:3005/api/secret
Authorization: Bearer admin-token-123

### Same secret without token → 401 from auth middleware.
GET http://localhost:3005/api/secret
